OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FA man has been convicted of shooting a
OL,7,F15-year-old boy dead in a children's
OL,8,Fplay area during a family music
OL,9,Ffestival at a London park.
OL,11,FAderahman Boumzough, 25, of no fixed
OL,12,Faddress, was found guilty of murdering
OL,13,FRene Graham and the attempted murder
OL,14,Fof a man at Woolwich Crown Court on
OL,15,FFriday.
OL,17,FMore than a year passed before
OL,18,FBoumzough was arrested and charged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
