OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782634701
OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FPolice were called to Emslie
OL,7,FHorniman's Pleasance Park in Ladbroke
OL,8,FGrove, west London, at around 7.20pm
OL,9,Fon July 21 2024.
OL,11,FCCTV footage showed Boumzough "calmly
OL,12,Fapproaching" the children's play area
OL,13,Fduring a family music festival before
OL,14,Ffiring a single shot, the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice said in a statement on Saturday.
OL,17,FFurther footage showed him chasing and
OL,18,Fattempting to shoot a man, but the gun
OL,19,Fjammed and he fled, it added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
