OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FHis phone was found to contain a video
OL,7,Fof him appearing to rap about the
OL,8,Ffirearm jamming, saying: "Don't you
OL,9,Fhate it when your ting jams? I was
OL,10,Fprepared to take soul, but Allah had a
OL,11,Fdifferent plan."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
