OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Alison
OL,7,FFoxwell, who led the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid after the verdicts: "While only a
OL,9,Fsmall number of people came forward, I
OL,10,Fwould like to thank those individuals
OL,11,Fwho provided statements and supported
OL,12,Fthe investigation, including attending
OL,13,Fcourt, who refused to allow a
OL,14,Fdangerous individual such as Boumzough
OL,15,Fto live amongst them."
OL,17,FA year after the murder, a #20,000
OL,18,Freward was posted for information
OL,19,Fleading to the arrest of those
OL,20,Fresponsible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
