OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FPolice also published further footage
OL,7,Fthat showed Boumzough pulling a
OL,8,Ffirearm from his pocket before fleeing
OL,9,Fthe scene and attempting to shoot the
OL,10,Fsecond victim as he escaped.
OL,12,FRene's mother, Janay John-Francois,
OL,13,Fmade a plea for help a month after her
OL,14,Fson died.
OL,16,FIn her statement through the Met, she
OL,17,Fsaid: "I cannot begin to describe the
OL,18,Fdepth of my pain after losing my
OL,19,Fprecious angel.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
