PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782634701
OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,F"The emptiness and heartbreak, there
OL,7,Fare no words that can capture the
OL,8,Fagony of my loss.
OL,10,F"This is a grief so profound I would
OL,11,Fnot wish it upon my worst enemy ` I've
OL,12,Flost everything, my world will never
OL,13,Fbe the same."
OL,15,FMs John-Francois also said: "Today is
OL,16,Fmy son, but tomorrow could be one of
OL,17,Fyours. Please stand with me through
OL,18,Fthe darkest of times."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
