OL,3,CMan convicted of shooting boy dead at
OL,4,CLondon play area in broad daylight
OL,6,FBoumzough was arrested on September 2
OL,7,F2025 and charged the following day
OL,8,Fwith murder and attempted murder.
OL,10,FHis trial lasted two weeks and he will
OL,11,Fbe sentenced on July 3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
